OL,4,Cautomate more work, Hays says
OL,6,FMr Way also said that ongoing worries
OL,7,Fabout the cost of living mean that
OL,8,Fworkers are not as confident to move
OL,9,Fjobs and companies are reluctant to
OL,10,Fhire.
OL,12,FThis is lengthening the time required
OL,13,Fto fill vacancies across all sectors,
OL,14,Fwhich the recruiter views as a key
OL,15,Findicator of the market.
