OL,3,CWage pressures pushing UK firms to
OL,4,Cautomate more work, Hays says
OL,6,F"Loyalty to your employer is no longer
OL,7,Fconsidered a valuable trait and people
OL,8,Fare eager to exercise control over
OL,9,Ftheir career, opting to deliver
OL,10,Fproject-based work rather than
OL,11,Fcommuting five days a week," he said.
OL,13,FAccompanying research by Hays showed
OL,14,Fthat the UK lags behind most of its
OL,15,Fpeers in terms of benefiting from
OL,16,Fworkforce investment, and how
OL,17,Fadaptable the labour market is to
OL,18,Fchanging business needs.
